olor:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi l\u00e0 si\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Barca, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i Lan &quot;troll&quot; phim v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/4.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Manchester United v\u1eeba c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Hoa K\u1ef3. Club America (Mexico), San Jose Earthquakes (M\u1ef9) l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man Utd trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"messi\" title=\"messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/tiet-lo-messi-giai-cuu-barca-du-chua-khoi-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Messi ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Opta, Lionel Messi l\u00e0 si\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a La Liga trong th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 21. V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Walter Pandiani (20 b\u00e0n), Messi \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 21 b\u00e0n khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i La Liga, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Egy Maulana Virki, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 &quot;Messi c\u1ee7a Indonesia&quot; d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Benfica theo d\u1ea1ng th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Lechia Gdansk (Ba Lan) tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng khi gia nh\u1eadp h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2/2018.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shay Given cho r\u1eb1ng Kevin De Bruyne x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah, b\u1edfi l\u1ebd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong s\u00e1ng nay (3/4), HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Samuel Eto'o d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed &quot;Young Africa&quot; khi \u0111\u0103ng tin t\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e2n ng\u00e0y n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i C\u00e1 th\u00e1ng T\u01b0 (1/4) v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua tranh c\u1eed T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Cameroon n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 1 b\u1ed9 phim n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu, Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. Tr\u00ean c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea3 h\u00ea khi cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng l\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phim sap ra mat ve bong da Viet Nam bi nguoi Thai danh gia khong cao.\" title=\"Phim s\u1eafp ra m\u1eaft v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng cao.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/diem-tin-toi-34-nguoi-thai-troll-phim-ve-bong-da-viet-nam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Phim s\u1eafp ra m\u1eaft v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng cao.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League 2017-18, Del Piero cho r\u1eb1ng &quot;b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&quot; \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Real trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi Acecook, VFF \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 lu\u1eadt c\u1ea5m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef3 t\u00f4m trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t b