t;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i Napoli v\u00e0 Juventus trong v\u00f2ng 5 n\u0103m qua. Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, cha Higuain ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid &ndash; CLB l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCha c\u1ee7a <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-juventus-kane-chua-the-so-sanh-voi-higuain-184-180125.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gonzalo Higuain</strong></span> m\u1edbi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn con trai \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid. Theo \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp; ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u00e0nh t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Thay v\u00ec Higuain ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i, anh b\u1ecb \u00e9p ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2006, Higuain r\u1eddi CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 River Plate \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh tr\u1ea3i qua kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi 6 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 3 La Liga. Tr\u1ea3i qua 6 m\u00f9a r\u01b0\u1ee1i, Higuain n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Real m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2013 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: 107 b\u00e0n sau 190 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cha Higuain phat bieu ve Real va cuoc chia tay qua khu hinh anh\" title=\"Cha Higuain ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chia tay qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Cha-Higuain-phat-bieu-ve-Real-va-cuoc-chia-tay-qua-khu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Higuain t\u1eebng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Napoli, Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 91 b\u00e0n sau 146 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00ednh ra, El Pipita \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trung b\u00ecnh h\u01a1n 30 b\u00e0n sau 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam Italia. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn Juventus m\u00ea m\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, Higuain ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua con s\u1ed1 54 b\u00e0n sau 95 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua. Higuain c\u00f9ng Juventus gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u Serie A v\u00e0 Coppa Italia m\u00f9a 2016/17 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League (thua 1-4 Real Madrid).</div>\r\n<h2>G\u00f3c khu\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh c\u1edd, t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-ngay-bau-vat-tro-ve-thanh-turin-184-183439.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Juventus g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Real Madrid</strong></span>. Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh El Larguero c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0i Cadena SER (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), cha Higuain ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn con trai m\u00ecnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"He lo nguyen nhan Higuain phai ban xoi khoi Real hinh anh 2\" title=\"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Higuain ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n x\u1edbi kh\u1ecfi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/cha-higuain-phat-bieu-ve-real-va-cuoc-chia-tay-qua-khu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Cha Higuain ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Khi Higuain r\u1eddi Real Madrid, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em>&rdquo;, cha ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00f3i. &ldquo;<em>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Perez kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch n\u00f3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Benzema, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain.</em> &rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00fang ra Higuain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid l\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Juventus vs Real Madrid\" title=\"Preview Juventus vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/HLV-Allegri-phat-bieu-ve-tran-dau-Juventus-vs-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus vs Real Madrid 1h45 ng\u00e0y 4/4</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-ngay-bau-vat-tro-ve-thanh-turin-184-183439.html\">Juventus vs Real Madrid: Ng\u00e0y &ldquo;b\u00e1u v\u1eadt&rdquo; tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh Turin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-allegri-canh-bao-real-juventus-da-truong-thanh-hon-rat-nhieu-184-183421.html\">HLV Allegri c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real: Juventus \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-01h45-ngay-44-chua-the-tra-thu-184-183419.html\">Juventus vs Real Madrid (01h45 ng\u00e0y 4/4): Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chiellini-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-than-trong-truoc-real-madrid-184-183417.html\">Chiellini ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo, th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid-184-183395.html\">Zidane c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/truoc-dai-chien-buffon-len-tieng-khen-ngoi-ronaldo-184-183123.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, Buffon l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"761","checkdouble":"183453"},{"date":"18:29 03/04","title":"Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Umtiti","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/9/16/barca-nhan-tin-buon-truoc-dai-chien-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;