0x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antoine Griezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/atletico-madrid-1390.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Atletico Madrid</strong></span>. HLV Ernesto Valverde mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti noi ve kha nang Antoine Griezmann toi Barca hinh anh\" title=\"Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Umtiti-noi-ve-kha-nang-Antoine-Griezmann-toi-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Griezmann duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-bat-ngo-tim-nha-o-thanh-pho-barcelona-180-179544.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111ang t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Barcelona</strong></span>, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Umtiti l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca mua Griezmann</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018: \u201cAnh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, Griezmann l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Barca\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti noi ve kha nang Antoine Griezmann toi Barca\" title=\"Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu 6 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u1ebfu Griezmann c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Griezmann s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUmtiti \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Barca: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Barca, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 CLB m\u00e0 t\u00f4i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i r\u1eddi Barca l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1eeb Xavi, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n anh \u1ea5y v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca</strong></span> mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/85859-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"759","checkdouble":"183457"},{"date":"16:54 03/04","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/12/chelsea-chon-allegri-thay-cho-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-wei