            <h3>Chelsea t\u00ednh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Allegri thay Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Premier League. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Blues c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m tham d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m cho Chelsea tr\u1edf n\u00ean thi\u1ebfu h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Max Allegri. V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd The Sun, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, Allegri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng sau khi chia tay Juventus. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd m\u1edbi chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean t\u1edd Telegraph: \u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf Italia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft r\u1ed3i\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a The Sun cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Allegri nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Chelsea. V\u00e0 Allegri s\u1ebd t\u1edbi London l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ngay khi tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi tay c\u1ee7a Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Allegri c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Juventus t\u1eeb tay Conte. V\u00e0 trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bianconeri, Allegri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League t\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve l\u1ecdt qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, <span href=\"HLV Allegri \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Premier League thay th\u1ebf cho Antonio Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea.\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Conte</span> s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 Chelsea \u0111ang lao d\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng phanh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang k\u00e9m top 4 t\u1edbi 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 khi Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang ngay trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-cho-mu-hoac-chelsea-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-183449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-cho-mu-hoac-chelsea-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-cho-mu-hoac-chelsea-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-183449.html\">Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alderweireld cho MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Chelsea trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 FA Cup. \u1ede s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 Southampton. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u FA Cup nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a The Blues. Nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i sai l\u1ea7m tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ecd suy y\u1ebfu kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"758","checkdouble":"183445"},{"date":"16:42 03/04","title":"\"Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Liverpool h\u1ea1 Man City \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/khong-bat-ngo-neu-liverpool-ha-man-city-de-vao-ban-ket-c1.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;