lpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh David James \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 The Kop cao h\u01a1n Man xanh.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premier League c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuu sao tuyen Anh dua ra nhan dinh Liverpool vs Man City  hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/khong-bat-ngo-neu-liverpool-ha-man-city-de-vao-ban-ket-c1.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool vs Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. MU, Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i khi\u1ebfn hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 2 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad, Man xanh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 5-0, c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i Anfield n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 3-4.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/pep-guardiola-thua-nhan-khong-co-cach-ngan-can-bo-ba-cua-liverpool-184-183375.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Pep d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool</strong></span>. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1ed9 ba Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David James \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Liverpool cao h\u01a1n Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00eam mai, Man City s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh David James chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City t\u1ea1i Anfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon David James\" title=\"thu mon David James\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/12/thu mon David James.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;David James \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City t\u1ea1i Anfield v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cao h\u01a1n Man City&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDavid James c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool </strong></span>ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 ai c\u1ea3. Ngay c\u1ea3 Bayern, Real hay Barca \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Liverpool, phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u00e1u l\u1eeda m\u00e0 Klopp \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Liverpool v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Man xanh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Everton 3-1 th\u00ec The Kop c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/truoc-tu-ket-cup-c1-nguoi-liverpool-lay-salah-ra-doa-man-city-184-183410.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Van Dijk \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng Salah \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111e d\u1ecda Man City</strong></span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"757","checkdouble":"183447"},{"date":"17:04 03/04","title":"Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alderweireld cho MU ho\u1eb7c Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-cho-mu-hoac-chelsea-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFo