: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nong Tottenham ban Toby Alderweireld neu thu ve 50 trieu bang hinh anh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Tottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Nong-Tottenham-ban-Toby-Alderweireld-neu-thu-ve-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Toby Alderweireld th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Davinson Sanchez v\u00e0 Jan Vertonghen.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Alderweireld ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo The Sun, c\u1ef1u sao Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Tottenham \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/psg-mua-trung-ve-alderweireld-197-183423.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alderweireld</strong></span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alderweireld n\u1ebfu\u2026</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/tottenham-hotspur-5.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tottenham </strong></span>b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea3 MU, Chelsea hay PSG \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toby Alderweireld cua tottenham\" title=\"Toby Alderweireld cua tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-mua-toby-alderweireld-cung-mu-va-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Tottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 180.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 s\u1ef1 chi tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/toby-alderweireld-54463.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Toby Alderweireld</strong></span> r\u1eddi Tottenham \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Toby Alderweireld \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/44575-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Toby Alderweireld \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=