n-squaresmall-plus{background-position:-48px -208px}.ui-icon-squaresmall-minus{background-position:-64px -208px}.ui-icon-squaresmall-close{background-position:-80px -208px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-vertical{background-position:0 -224px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-horizontal{background-position:-16px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-vertical{background-position:-32px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-horizontal{background-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ilkay Gundogan v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung t\u1ea1i Borussia Dortmund trong v\u00f2ng 4 n\u0103m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gundogan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Klopp v\u00e0 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 l\u1edbn trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-klopp-choi-don-tam-ly-voi-man-city-truoc-dai-chien-184-183373.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Jurgen Klopp</strong></span> c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ilkay Gundogan. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1eafc n\u1ee3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 khi Liverpool vs Man City t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGundogan \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Dortmund, CLB anh gia nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb Nurnberg v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011. Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng HLV Klopp v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd c\u00f9ng nhau gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2012/13.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gundogan phat bieu ve Klopp va mon no qua khu hinh anh\" title=\"Gundogan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Klopp v\u00e0 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Gundogan-phat-bieu-ve-Klopp-va-mon-no-qua-khu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gundogan v\u00e0 Klopp t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Dortmund</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n sang Man City t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2016/17, nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Gundogan. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng trong tay Guardiola. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League gi\u1eefa <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/khong-bat-ngo-neu-liverpool-ha-man-city-de-vao-ban-ket-c1-172-183447.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool vs Man City</strong></span>, Gundogan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Klopp v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Klopp\u201d, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Man City. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, \u0111i qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t tr\u1ea7m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn Dortmund t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ecf. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n trong 6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng. T\u00f4i h\u01a1i nh\u00fat nh\u00e1t v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Klopp v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tro cu len tieng ve mon no cuc lon voi Klopp hinh anh 2\" title=\"Tr\u00f2 c\u0169 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Klopp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/gundogan-phat-bieu-ve-klopp-va-mon-no-qua-khu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Gundogan ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Klopp v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sao-man-city-giai-thich-ly-do-tu-choi-hoi-ngo-klopp-172-181651.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ilkay Gundogan</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb Klopp v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cT\u00f4i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man City. \u201c\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKlopp \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Jurgen Klopp tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-klopp-choi-don-tam-ly-voi-man-city-truoc-dai-chien-184-183373.html\">HLV Klopp ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f2n t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1edbi Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-chan-thuong-lallana-172-183253.html\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Lallana l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp-172-183242.html\">Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool: 90 ph\u00fat nh\u1edb \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u201cThe Klopp\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-khien-liverpool-lo-sot-vo-vi-tha-thinh-bayern-munich-172-183088.html\">Klopp khi\u1ebfn Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u00ec \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hlv-klopp-172-182995.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Klopp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_ur